prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card. A whimsical and humorous fantasy beach scene. In the foreground, illustrated versions of Lao Lao (from the left of the reference photo) and Jordan (from the right) are building an absurdly elaborate sandcastle together. Lao Lao, wearing her light blue sweatshirt and black pants, is meticulously placing a tiny seashell flag on the highest turret with a focused, slightly mischievous smile. Jordan, wearing his tan hoodie and dark pants, is comically struggling to carry a giant, oversized bucket filled with shimmering, magical water that is sloshing over the sides. The sandcastle is fantastical, with spiraling towers, glowing windows, and tiny crabs wearing party hats scuttling around its base.

The beach itself is magical: the sand sparkles with iridescent glitter, the ocean waves are gentle and glow with soft bioluminescence, and the sky is a dreamy twilight lavender with constellations shaped like birthday cakes and balloons. Two playful dolphins with party hats on are leaping out of the water in the background.

Centered in the sky above them is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script. The overall style is dreamy, ethereal, and fantastical with a lighthearted, funny tone.
